{"tid":1426740,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林忌：劉細良唔係泛民。分化撚咪玩野。","createTime":"2019-08-07T03:38:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T06:32:42.000Z","uid":134071,"like":87,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"308dc75303fe02dfcb9b1bab98575aff2658917e","tid":1426740,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:38:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/9gOmFOV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9gOmFOV.jpg&h=75f755e1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156132813336121&amp;id=700986120\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10156132813336121%26id%3D700986120&d=QE5rvD4iboeChbAAuj3apAqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=6e678249\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10156132813336121&amp;id=700986120</a>"},{"pid":"c533de2a9ce35514997c9d9b5285feb38e5393da","tid":1426740,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86c058a0a07d044c6f2addbe142229c8a65e0f1d","tid":1426740,"uid":108347,"like":108,"dislike":10,"score":98,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T03:48:04.000Z","msg":"劉細良分柝冇錯，佢只係行動方向同勇武唔同，佢的確講到中共個劇本出嚟，至於行動，我只係希望大家真係諗清楚效果先，唔好為發洩而發洩<br />\n<br />\n好簡單，你噴黑部狗車，佢轉個頭就車狗去打人，你攻車軩佢就半日用唔到部車，你係狗屋門口放火，佢叫消防嚟救，但係鎖尻佢門，佢要自己攪，有泥水佬仲可以起到半米到一米高嘅牆"},{"pid":"68c242ae93ec4e8912ed482643abf95ecafa7b8d","tid":1426740,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f845c9a2624b6fccd87a3767892765fb2ea912","tid":1426740,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:20:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76d275d3cb7f1b7e8c3d84ab6b07b2d3fac28004","tid":1426740,"uid":46078,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:21:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dax3dWH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fdax3dWH.jpg&h=b4233ccb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9rjk0BJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9rjk0BJ.jpg&h=1bcc246a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YbOFf94.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYbOFf94.jpg&h=91aa4b04&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q2g3Yop.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ2g3Yop.jpg&h=0f561caa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9b6287c6dd910b3990204bb6a0cfc045950fcabb","tid":1426740,"uid":289349,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"林忌有無上過前線?出過集會?"},{"pid":"afe7ef6083ac80b585debf4475f0f9770b3e22ef","tid":1426740,"uid":4783,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"9b6287c6dd910b3990204bb6a0cfc045950fcabb","tid":1426740,"uid":289349,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"林忌有無上過前線?出過集會?"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"我淨係知劉細良叫人改口號<br />\n呢樣已經on9到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點spin都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebc8843600e026abdbb8c321151d2059c7607e18","tid":1426740,"uid":134071,"like":15,"dislike":6,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"9b6287c6dd910b3990204bb6a0cfc045950fcabb","tid":1426740,"uid":289349,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"林忌有無上過前線?出過集會?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:23:02.000Z","msg":"唔好再胡亂話「xxx無上場，去左邊度」<br />\n<br />\n今次反送中，其實有為少不少既「名人」上前線，而又唔爭取光環：當中包括左中右既「名人」。<br />\n有唔少名人更係「蒙面」發夢！（靈通朋友聽到一些義士人名， 都好驚奇。）<br />\n<br />\n所以如果反送中抗爭成功， 係所有人所有派別既功勞。<br />\n<br />\n（但當然， 何式凝呢d人依然要照鬧）"},{"pid":"f3a8012b5df9860edb8cb8623098637d225316b3","tid":1426740,"uid":221265,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afe7ef6083ac80b585debf4475f0f9770b3e22ef","tid":1426740,"uid":4783,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"9b6287c6dd910b3990204bb6a0cfc045950fcabb","tid":1426740,"uid":289349,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"林忌有無上過前線?出過集會?"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"我淨係知劉細良叫人改口號<br />\n呢樣已經on9到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點spin都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:23:32.000Z","msg":"你睇晒人哋講乜先啦<br />\n睇前文後理啦"},{"pid":"a2dd317bdd64d376fda4c64d5ca00c300e78171e","tid":1426740,"uid":289349,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"afe7ef6083ac80b585debf4475f0f9770b3e22ef","tid":1426740,"uid":4783,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"9b6287c6dd910b3990204bb6a0cfc045950fcabb","tid":1426740,"uid":289349,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"林忌有無上過前線?出過集會?"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"我淨係知劉細良叫人改口號<br />\n呢樣已經on9到無朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點spin都無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:26:31.000Z","msg":"甘咪繼續卑人扣帽子?"},{"pid":"7ef3ef71aeeb33ed936b431317b76736f7590c9c","tid":1426740,"uid":289349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f3a8012b5df9860edb8cb8623098637d225316b3","tid":1426740,"uid":221265,"like":9,"dislike":9,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afe7ef6083ac80b585debf4475f0f9770b3e22ef","tid":1426740,"uid":4783,"like":29,"dislike":4,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"9b6287c6dd910b3990204bb6a0cfc045950fcabb","tid":1426740,"uid":289349,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T16:22:15.000Z","msg"